    "description": [
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "  CH.05 · THE BEASTS",
      "◆━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━◆",
      "",
      "▸ The world has 89 creatures you haven't seen yet.",
      "  Some are passive. Most are not.",
      "  Some can be tamed.",
      "  All of them drop something.",
      "",
      "◈ ALEX'S MOBS — HIGHLIGHTS",
      "  └ Void Worm: End boss, spawns in The End",
      "    drops unique void materials",
      "  └ Platypus: passive, drops venomous spur",
      "    (venom used in advanced poison recipes)",
      "  └ Raccoon: tameable with sweet berries",
      "    carries small items in its hands",
      "  └ Enderiophage: found in The End",
      "    drops rare ender materials",
      "  └ Blobfish: ocean depths, drops rare fish item",
      "  └ Bone Serpent: Nether, dangerous, drops",
      "    serpent scales for armor",
      "",
      "◈ ECOLOGICS — HIGHLIGHTS",
      "  └ 24+ documented creature variants",
      "  └ Coconut Crab: beach mob, drops crab claws",
      "  └ Mangrove Treefrog: passive, ambient",
      "  └ Sandy Rabbit: desert variant",
      "  └ Capybara: river/swamp, passive, tameable",
      "",
      "◈ SCROLL: The Beasts",
      "  └ Found in: wilderness ruins, hunter's lodge,",
      "    rare beast kill drops (5%), naturalist journal chest",
      "  └ Research time: 20 min",
      "  └ Unlocks: Alex's Mobs awareness, tameable creature list",
      "",
      "▸ The Scholars who wrote the scrolls sent",
      "  expeditions to document every creature.",
      "  Most expeditions came back.",
      "  Not all of them came back complete.",
      "",
      "▶ Find The Beasts scroll [check]",
      "▶ Tame or befriend an Alex's Mobs/Ecologics creature [check]",
      "",
      "◇ The Void Worm (Alex's Mobs) and the Ender Trigon",
      "  both spawn in The End. Ch14 addresses them.",
      "  Don't go to The End unprepared."
